rComments: Theoretical-based teaching was fine, application-based teaching was very poor. Be prepared to watch many Youtube tutorials as opposed to learning HOW to do anything IN class. He is very patient and willing to help though. Just be prepared for a lot of self-learning.
Evan knows his stuff, though could teach more of the application and use of the programs, as well as give material for students to follow along.
teacherRatingTags: ['Get ready to read', 'Test heavy', 'Graded by few things']
